54:49.372 --> 54:54.047
<i>♪♪♪</i>

54:54.048 --> 54:54.984
Oh, there they are.

54:57.823 --> 55:00.227
- I don't understand this.
- I know.

55:02.064 --> 55:03.366
- Hey, there they are.
- Let's go!

55:03.367 --> 55:04.435
Dr. and Mrs. Masters.

55:04.436 --> 55:05.604
Come on!

55:05.605 --> 55:08.777
