55:08.778 --> 55:10.981
Couple of shots! Right here, right here.

55:10.982 --> 55:12.685
- Turn around!
- Don't be shy!

55:12.686 --> 55:15.424
I suppose we could give
them just one photo.

55:15.425 --> 55:17.027
Don't you think, Bill?

55:17.028 --> 55:18.764
MAN: We're all trying
to make a living here.

55:18.765 --> 55:19.999
MAN: Yeah, we're just
trying to make a buck, huh?

55:20.000 --> 55:21.101
Quick shot.

55:21.102 --> 55:22.505
That's it, Virginia.

55:22.506 --> 55:24.174
- Nice, two more.
- Come on.

55:24.175 --> 55:29.185
<i>♪♪♪</i>

55:31.122 --> 55:32.793
Dr. and Mrs. Masters.

55:34.195 --> 55:37.367
Gentlemen, it's Masters and Johnson.

55:37.368 --> 55:39.137
That's who we are.

